// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0242 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 946fe707-771d-5d29-b210-f7f538d55e27

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:18.04-ESM*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:20.04-ESM*")
